&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;本体部&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;img src=&#34;https://shiiiiiiiii1.github.io/PortfolioSiteHugo/PortfolioSiteHugo/img/portfolio/kettle_design7.jpg&#34; width=&#34;40%&#34;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;土台部&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;img src=&#34;https://shiiiiiiiii1.github.io/PortfolioSiteHugo/PortfolioSiteHugo/img/portfolio/kettle_design8.png&#34; width=&#34;40%&#34;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

